{{! Static placeholder for the subnav center slot during cold-load
    substates. Index routes can't render their live subnav controls
    while the controller is still being set up, but yielding nothing
    collapses the bar and causes a layout jump when the real subnav
    pops in after the model resolves. This skeleton holds the row at
    the same height with neutral pulse blocks. }}
<div class="controls" aria-hidden="true">
  <div
    class="h-9 w-64 max-w-full animate-pulse rounded bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800"
  ></div>
  <div
    class="h-9 w-24 animate-pulse rounded bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800"
  ></div>
</div>